OL,3,C'Deeply sorry': Hospital trust
OL,4,Capologies to parents in maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FDerby and Burton Hospital Trust say
OL,8,Fthey are "deeply sorry" to the
OL,9,Ffamilies they "let down" during an
OL,10,Finvestigation into the deaths of more
OL,11,Fthan 150 babies'.
OL,13,FThe review has found numerous "care
OL,14,Fissues" may have contributed to the
OL,15,Fdeaths, according to the Local
OL,16,FDemocracy Reporting Service.
OL,18,FThe review focused on deaths between
OL,19,FJanuary 2020 and March 2023.
