OL,3,C'Deeply sorry': Hospital trust
OL,4,Capologies to parents in maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FThe Trust says: "We have made
OL,8,Fsignificant improvements to our
OL,9,Fmaternity and neonatal services, and
OL,10,Fare providing safer care than we were
OL,11,F18 months ago, with better outcomes
OL,12,Ffor mothers and babies."
OL,14,FThis has come in the shadow of a
OL,15,Freport from the Care and Quality
OL,16,FCommission (CQC) saying they fear poor
OL,17,Fmaternity care will become
OL,18,F"normalised" if action isn't taken.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
