OL,3,C'Deeply sorry': Hospital trust
OL,4,Capologies to parents in maternity
OL,5,Creview
OL,7,FOf the 131 units inspected between
OL,8,FAugust 2022 and December 2023, almost
OL,9,Fhalf (48%) were rated as "requires
OL,10,Fimprovement" or "inadequate".
OL,12,FOnly 4% were classed as "outstanding"
OL,13,Fand 48% were rated as "good".
OL,15,FThese failures of care, described as
OL,16,F"systemic" in the report, were
OL,17,Finitially levelled at Telford and
OL,18,FShrewsbury Hospital Trust two years
OL,19,Fago.
